snippet.title: Resident Evil 3 OUT NOW | Intro [GOG]
snippet.description:
Resident Evil 3 returns! Only on GOG!
The 3rd part of the series that defined the survival horror genre is now available on GOG – uncut, compatible with modern machines, and scarier than ever...
Own a piece of history and play it offline today!

Buy now: https://bit.ly/3XTF81y
